# 1. Force detection for your core languages
*.py linguist-language=Python
*.rs linguist-language=Rust
*.sh linguist-detectable=true
Dockerfile linguist-detectable=true

# 2. Hide things that are likely causing the "Other" bloat
# This moves them out of the language stats entirely
*.json linguist-vendored
*.txt linguist-vendored
*.md linguist-documentation
LICENSE linguist-documentation